         ntp,
         python (>= 2.7),
         snmpd,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: NorNet Tunnelbox Control
 This package contains the scripts to configure the tunnelboxes of NorNet
 sites.
 .
 See http://www.nntb.no for details on NorNet!

Package: nornet-node
